# Perform these checks before releasing a version

% git status
- no extra files

% prove -I lib xt t

% cover -t
- must exceed 70%

% ./apache.cgi
- http://localhost:8000/cgi
- Click on ALL cgis
- http://localhost:8000/perl/

% plackup example/09*
- http://localhost:5000/
- no "unimplemented" show up

% plackup example/07*
- http://localhost:5000/wiki
- search
- click
- edit an article

# got here - commit!

% grep -r VERSION lib
- version-bump ALL except 0.0x (didn't change since last release)
- edit Changes
- edit TODO - remove completed, add new, sort by target version

% git commit -m "^_^ Version X.XX released NOCODE"

% git tag v.X.XX -m "Version X.XX released"

% git push && git push --tags
